<p id="_19822ada-e66c-171f-ab24-d5fc6d38dbf8"><strong>iii.   Preface</strong><note id="_69be0319-6d01-5f38-0502-5b64b88e0c45"><p id="_a24502da-8c5a-9054-9bd2-c93cfae0773d">Insert Preface Text here. Give OGC specific commentary: describe the technical content, reason for document, history of the document and precursors, and plans for future work. &gt; Attention is drawn to the possibility that some of the elements of this document may be the subject of patent rights. The Open Geospatial Consortium shall not be held responsible for identifying any or all such patent rights.</p>

