<clause id="_05889770-164c-1b66-a7b7-db4aff7eec6a" obligation="normative">
<title id="_8abe5390-8bdc-b693-eba8-397de170c370">Conceptual Emission Event Model</title>
<p id="_d8cd2729-c4c6-8ef3-759c-eb1a92adf4ca">The EmissionML conceptual model is described as a class diagram in Figure x. The schema is fully described in x.x.x.</p>

<p id="_71933ab3-c497-69e0-5e73-dcbad935008b">Use the following table for Requirements Classes.</p>

<table id="_229a309b-afed-1d3e-380d-51623f3624a5" width="90%"><colgroup><col width="20%"/><col width="80%"/></colgroup><tbody><tr id="_ba85d06d-c1cc-ff86-ab7b-ad549dc780db"><td id="_c2567bc3-4e7a-807e-2201-d1c449320cb5" colspan="2" valign="middle" align="left"><strong>Emission Event Conceptual Data Model Core</strong> </td>
</tr><tr id="_b59cfb88-9464-7ea1-80ee-1b15b47c5445"><td id="_3e64eea5-bd3e-c319-9565-c96bf45730ea" colspan="2" valign="middle" align="left"><link target="http://www.opengis.net/spec/emissionml/1.0/req/datamodel/core"/> </td>
</tr><tr id="_231963f7-4418-129c-44fe-62dcf975d461"><td id="_0a69611d-41a9-9773-f576-65c1b16b693a" valign="middle" align="left">Target type</td>
<td id="_890f0fb8-e01d-f16d-253e-c95add6522b5" valign="middle" align="left">Data Model</td>
</tr><tr id="_aca30b07-0fff-0cfb-25f8-6d354215fe12"><td id="_ac7f756c-9c84-fe34-fe3c-3d2e68410e7a" valign="middle" align="left">Dependency</td>
<td id="_bf218e58-54fc-7587-d738-202a92aeb653" valign="middle" align="left"><link target="http://www.opengis.net/spec//req/obs-cpt/Observation"/></td>
</tr><tr id="_de754a20-c1eb-61d6-e2bf-b0fcfee0d6a2"><td id="_d13cd440-69c5-a06c-c54b-b23d7dc056f3" valign="middle" align="left"><strong>Requirement 1</strong> </td>
<td id="_6bd92e4d-eaf6-5d4f-aeea-c24bdd2209b7" valign="middle" align="left"><link target="http://www.opengis.net/spec/emissionml/1.0/req/datamodel/core/emission-event"/><br/> requirement description tbc </td>
</tr><tr id="_d57bac06-2898-f50c-90bc-fda86e014887"><td id="_0eab7395-22c4-0cb9-5a40-9657020ecfed" valign="middle" align="left"><strong>Requirement 2</strong> </td>
<td id="_a18c56da-3ed7-01e4-75a6-046b828cb2ef" valign="middle" align="left"><link target="http://www.opengis.net/spec/emissionml/1.0/req/datamodel/core/source"/><br/> requirement description tbc </td>
</tr><tr id="_0147840b-af0a-161e-6177-21b787cecf34"><td id="_d3fcc427-fbbe-4106-d430-c6cc1bc9a951" valign="middle" align="left"><strong>Requirement 3</strong> </td>
<td id="_352a3cd1-70ac-8d2e-f834-7698e7042619" valign="middle" align="left"><link target="http://www.opengis.net/spec/emissionml/1.0/req/datamodel/core/mechanism"/><br/> requirement description tbc </td>
</tr><tr id="_7b7d763e-4e23-0610-35d8-82f03d01a688"><td id="_ee399d07-c79e-e96a-86dd-7b576d28e04b" valign="middle" align="left"><strong>Requirement 4</strong> </td>
<td id="_ae94d8ce-9ac8-4e0d-21c6-ce7c03f316d2" valign="middle" align="left"><link target="http://www.opengis.net/spec/emissionml/1.0/req/datamodel/core/emission-quantity"/><br/> requirement description tbc </td>
</tr><tr id="_34d31d95-b256-a539-ca04-dfe5e2d10ecd"><td id="_491342b8-38b4-a700-e182-b7b400d6a470" valign="middle" align="left"><strong>Requirement 5</strong> </td>
<td id="_5e99bd3b-525e-2ff5-d7e2-bb7427e5c4be" valign="middle" align="left"><link target="http://www.opengis.net/spec/emissionml/1.0/req/datamodel/core/start-time"/><br/> requirement description tbc </td>
