<clause id="_d7134465-4454-8d72-aa61-a0d518f05ddf" obligation="normative">
<title id="_ff08b688-274b-5e87-11b5-5afab06ab175">Source Class</title>
<p id="_5d754275-f2b5-45d3-9748-71fb08b0997b">A Source represents the feature from which an emission originates. A Source includes a geometry and may include a name.</p>

<table id="_8dbe4b14-e879-6976-894c-312f971927d5" width="“90%”"><tbody><tr id="_6d081ce5-e7b0-cd5c-21f5-56a498ef7955"><td id="_6b105d4e-9af1-6f21-2919-99f8ff2ae2bf" valign="middle" align="left">Requirement 6: Source Class </td>
<td id="_9ebb43f4-dca9-ed36-3294-0b086e28aea1" valign="middle" align="left">/req/datamodel/core/source<br/> + Each Source class shall have the mandatory attributes listed in &lt;source-attributes&gt;. Each Source class shall have the direct relation between a Source class and other classes listed in &lt;source-relations&gt;.</td>
</tr></tbody>
</table>

<table id="_e9e01a6b-964b-360b-2e90-733149f5d5a8" anchor="source-attributes" width="“90%”">
<name id="_ee5c8f94-37ee-2ff4-99b7-0f1aecb18b49">Attributes of a Source class</name>
