<td id="_acda5d3a-7d2e-0e9e-4a20-f378576d1949" valign="middle" align="left">Definition</td>
<td id="_478fa477-2d19-2da8-0fbd-e1103dfc36ac" valign="middle" align="left">Data types and values</td>
