</clause>

<clause id="_85b9c357-d4c3-a48d-7ed9-6f422efb3202" obligation="normative">
<title id="_fe45ed34-1ab4-ec1a-1327-8951170f4805">Mechanism</title>
<p id="_3e9ab209-bc94-b62c-a4c2-3270d60bddff">A Mechanism is a code list that describes the mechanism by which an emission occurs.</p>
</clause>

<clause id="_3d6b073f-b74d-1e4e-205d-67723de5242a" obligation="normative">
<title id="_ccc9aae9-dcda-1578-e9cf-ae815fa4d62c">EmissionQuanity</title>
<table id="_33889972-5461-277d-ce71-dae87ad7ea79" width="90%"><colgroup><col width="25%"/><col width="75%"/></colgroup><tbody><tr id="_ddbbe31e-3ba0-120f-e352-3e8a7178461a"><td id="_40ed0b72-fb95-59c3-a3cc-16515f0229e3" valign="middle" align="left">Requirement 6: Source Class </td>
<td id="_7b5064f2-0d9c-478d-93e9-479215e48ef5" valign="middle" align="left">/req/datamodel/core/source<br/> + Each Source class shall have the mandatory attributes listed in  <xref target="source-attributes"/>. Each Source class shall have the direct relation between a Source class and other classes listed in  <xref target="source-relations"/>.</td>
</tr></tbody>
</table>

