<clause id="_c018a8c0-2abc-695c-10b9-2379bdfda733" obligation="normative">
<title id="_bbd518d1-9927-a5f1-5f5b-886196b31098">Determination Method Class</title>
<p id="_bd2636db-05bc-4372-0bbf-e40936dac0fc">A Determination Method describes how a value (e.g., an emission quantity or temporal bound) was determined. It provides a label and an optional URI linking to an external definition.</p>

<table id="_7be363a0-b272-a316-5c6f-6da13f78a8ac" width="“90%”"><tbody><tr id="_4e7951f4-32d8-46c6-fb8a-c4186fee9c2e"><td id="_82028cdd-d695-b6a8-e90e-7e34e80c78e4" valign="middle" align="left">Requirement 9: Determination Method Class </td>
<td id="_8595a38d-b434-3efa-6768-19dd609eadea" valign="middle" align="left">/req/datamodel/core/determination-method<br/> + Each Determination Method class shall have the mandatory attributes listed in &lt;&gt;. Each Determination Method class shall have the direct relation between a Determination Method class and other classes listed in &lt;&gt;.</td>
</tr></tbody>
</table>

<table id="_a8945a68-b787-dcaf-830b-c64c54d0f2e5" anchor="determination-method-attributes" width="“90%”">
<name id="_762118e8-e28b-a70a-0d98-0bc197eeb3ba">Attributes of a Determination Method class</name>
<tbody><tr id="_1587cb43-aea4-67d9-e2df-8ee98a1b05ec"><td id="_596ba758-be97-3030-b1a9-48b5633fdd69" valign="middle" align="left">Names</td>
<td id="_91b44d85-746d-eb28-420c-b15d8c3fbfb7" valign="middle" align="left">Definition</td>
<td id="_476f6a95-90ff-6bbb-98f4-8b976dfe5cf9" valign="middle" align="left">Data types and values</td>
<td id="_fd1df0af-456e-2998-1be1-5d440d206c6f" valign="middle" align="left">Multiplicity and use</td>
</tr><tr id="_c3f8f228-e05f-f9e1-2717-1b371bc1617a"><td id="_de2ad36c-0982-7019-6836-bea3ed0630c7" valign="middle" align="left">label</td>
<td id="_604b211c-3766-8ca5-e7c5-63a99494aa3c" valign="middle" align="left">A human-readable label for the determination method.</td>
<td id="_ce2aa303-bb66-ecde-e08c-0e076aab71d0" valign="middle" align="left">String</td>
<td id="_2b0c6de7-6b6e-23c6-942a-d500db8332e3" valign="middle" align="left">1 (mandatory)</td>
</tr><tr id="_58ba3a47-5525-41f1-73fa-8df50329b25a"><td id="_912cbdb5-b4af-bb6e-e748-dedb5e340016" valign="middle" align="left">definition</td>
