<title id="_fee9b0fb-8054-a631-0e37-9ad3f9d4ffe5">Bibliography</title>
<note id="_b7c04aa2-c1a9-1c9f-37f1-41f641910ab3"><p id="_7c4da3b1-200f-d075-126a-dae59ec827d9">The TC has approved Springer LNCS as the official document citation type.</p>

<p id="_6526fe1c-1b09-b27b-9fe8-2a2ce7997bc4">Springer LNCS is widely used in technical and computer science journals and other publications</p>


<p id="_c215cc32-ca20-c692-7269-8030fec8bf1a">– Actual References:</p>

<p id="_cf21a9a5-4fb0-1527-bf81-e0fef24a18a3">[n] Journal: Author Surname, A.: Title. Publication Title. Volume number, Issue number, Pages Used (Year Published)</p>
<index><primary>Example</primary></index></note>



